title: Virginia Tech Hokies' ACC women's basketball tournament run ends without star Elizabeth Kitley in loss to NC State - ESPN
content: Virginia Tech Hokies' ACC women's basketball tournament run ends without star Elizabeth Kitley in loss to NC State  ESPN
description: Virginia Tech's historic run in the ACC women's basketball tournament ended with a 70-55 loss to NC State in the quarterfinals on Friday, as star Elizabeth Kitley missed the game with a shoulder injury.
